extends layout

block content
  h1 getHashRate
  p This call will return network information of the Atheios chain. The result is averaged over the recent 4 blocks.
  h2 Parameters
  p None
  h2 Returns
  p getHashRate returns hashrate in MH/s rounded
  p getDifficulty returns current difficulty
  p getBlockTime returns current blocktime
  h2 Example
  .alert.alert-info(role="alert")
    | $ curl "https://api.atheios.org/api/getHashRate"
  .alert.alert-info(role="info")
    | {
    br
    |  "getHashRate": 1401,
    br
    |  "getDifficulty": "26839542111",
    br
    |  "getBlockTime": 19
    br
    |  }